If so, the numerous emendations proposed cannot be seriously con- sidered as even plausible restorations of the archetypon. But quite apart from this, most of these conjectures, on their authors' own admission, can only refer to a statement of Messalla in a Subsequent speech, which he at this stage of the discussion clearly had no intention of delivering.
